                           <locus/>Fol. 54va (below the text): Mention of the commissioner.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 54va: ሠርፀ፡ ድንግል፡ በዘሙኑ[sic]፡ ለዝ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘመካን፡ ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ወእሱረ፡ ይኩን፡ ኣሜን።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note, written in a secondary hand, mentions the name Śärḍä Dǝngǝl. A person with the same name (over erasure) is mentioned as the commissioner of the book in the note on fol. 7va.
